videos.headline: Bellarmine has the hot hand as they drain 3 consecutive 3-pointers
videos.description: Dylan Penn, Juston Betz and Curt Hopf waste no time as they knock down the long ball consecutively to give the Knights the lead in the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Bellarmine has the hot hand as they drain 3 consecutive 3-pointers) 2022/03/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Osayi Osifo somehow gets the reverse layup to fall for Jacksonville
videos.description: Osayi Osifo gets around his defender and drains the basket to pull the Dolphins within three.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Osayi Osifo gets the lay-in to fall vs. Bellarmine Knights) 2022/03/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rod Brown muscles through his defender for a Jacksonville and-1
videos.description: Rod Brown hauls in the dime from Kevion Nolan and knocks down the and-1 for the Dolphins.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Rod Brown muscles through his defender for a Jacksonville and-1) 2022/03/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Juston Betz drains the smooth layup for Bellarmine
videos.description: Justin Betz is smooth as silk as he puts a few moves on his defender and knocks down the basket to extend the Knights' lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Juston Betz drains the smooth layup for Bellarmine) 2022/03/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: CJ Fleming pulls up and knocks down the 3 for Bellarmine
videos.description: CJ Fleming has the crowd on its feet as he buries the triple for the Knights.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (CJ Fleming pulls up and knocks down the 3 for Bellarmine) 2022/03/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bellarmine's CJ Fleming drains wild one-legged 3 in crunch time
videos.description: CJ Fleming is unstoppable as he beats the shot clock with an incredible 3-pointer to extend the Knights' lead late in the second half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Bellarmine's CJ Fleming drains wild one-legged 3 in crunch time) 2022/03/08 ESHEET
